DISCLAIMER
The data is supplied on the basis that it is accurate to the best of Auckland Council knowledge and belief. While Auckland Council has exercised all reasonable skill and care in compiling and providing this data, Auckland Council accepts no liability in contract, tort or otherwise howsoever, for any loss, damage, injury or expense (whether direct, indirect or consequential) arising out of the provision of this data or its use by you.
NOTE ON DATA
Data users are cautioned to consider carefully the nature of this data before using it for decisions that concern personal or public safety or the conduct of business that involves monetary or operational consequences.
Data users are cautioned to consider carefully using or interpreting this data for purposes other than that for which it was collected.  Auckland Council should be consulted to verify whether the data is being correctly interpreted.
DATA QUALITY
Data provided may include both measured and synthesised data. Measured data may also include data of different quality. Please request quality codes with your data set if you wish to identify these types of data.
